To install:

1) Check you have the following installed:
   - Parallel::ForkManager (libparallel-forkmanager-perl
     package under GNU/Debian)
   - Getopt::Std (part of the standard Perl distribution)
   - Time::HiRes (part of the standard Perl distribution)
   - File::Basename (part of the standard Perl distribution)
   - IO::Socket::UNIX (part of the standard Perl distribution)
2) Make sure UNIXSocketScanner.pl is executable (chmod u+x
   UNIXSocketScanner.pl)

The latest version of UNIXSocketScanner can always be found at
<http://www.nth-dimension.org.uk/>.
